				<wikidot:authorName>psul</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2156983</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>If one was going to write this contest as crack fic (and in a three way contest, with these three to juggle, I'm not sure what other options one has), then I can't imagine it going much better than this! The conceit of Agent Diego following Quixote from disaster to disaster, as a framework for the story, also seems most effective.</p> 
				 	]]>
