				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7441755/down-with-the-sickness#post-3965232</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 11 Sep 2018 09:36:56 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Connor MacWarren</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3741977</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>SCP-049 lifts his head and meets the intruder's gaze. Blood drips from the needle-like tip of his &quot;nose&quot;.</p> <p>Don Quixote stands at the doorway, sword in hand: &quot;My God. She was right — you're the biggest mosquito I've ever seen!&quot;</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p>&quot;Thank you. And, um… I really like your proboscis. ~&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p>This is so stupid.</p> <p>+1.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
